    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。feature分支的order要设为0，这样它会在main的左侧显示。确认一下分支顺序：feature是0，main保持默认的1对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature order: 0",
        "mainBranchOrder: 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这样feature在左、main在右比较清晰。接下来main要提交b，然后切到feature提交i，再回到main继续提交c和d。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit b",
        "commit i",
        "commit c",
        "commit d",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这几个提交画好了。现在feature和main是并行开发的状态，feature有i，main有b、c、d。接下来怎么合并？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit i",
        "commit b",
        "commit c",
        "commit d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在feature分支上合并main，把main的最新进展同步到feature里。然后切回main继续提交e和f作为最终版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge main",
        "commit e",
        "commit f"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：merge操作是在feature分支上执行的，所以箭头是从main指向feature对吗？还有，需要显示分支名称和提交标签吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge main",
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel"
